1: HEAD± | 2: log | 3: main…± | 4: remote⇅ | 5: summary | 6: pr [N/M]
Enter: switch | Tab/alt-1…6: preview | alt-c: create | Esc:

Configure [commit.generation] command to enable LLM summari

Example in ~/.config/worktrunk/config.toml:

[commit.generation]
command = "llm -m haiku"

[list]
summary = true
